>
  <div class="card__content">
    <div class="card__summary">
      <h3 id="title-judiciary-launches-new-federal-ticket-processing-website">
        <a href="/2023/05/02/judiciary-launches-new-federal-ticket-processing-website/">Judiciary Launches New Federal Ticket Processing Website</a>
      </h3>
      <p>Individuals can now pay tickets for minor federal violations more easily, using a redesigned website for the Judiciary’s Central Violations Bureau. The website, officially launched in early May, leverages new technologies and best design practices to improve usability and accessibility across devices, including smart phones.
          <em class="card__source source"
            >— via
            <a
              href="https://www.uscourts.gov/news/2023/05/02/judiciary-launches-new-federal-ticket-processing-website"
