<article
  class="card card-elsewhere card-linked"
  data-edit-this="news/2023/05/2023-05-03-the-18f-design-chapter.md"
  
  aria-labelledby="title-the-18f-design-chapter"
>
  <div class="card__content">
    <div class="card__summary">
      <h3 id="title-the-18f-design-chapter">
        <a href="/2023/05/02/the-18f-design-chapter/">The 18F design chapter</a>
      </h3>
      <p>Designing technology-enabled public services requires deep expertise in how different elements of the experience come together (or don’t!). The 18F design chapter comprises four discipline-specific cohorts — service design, user experience (UX) design, product design, and content strategy — each of which has a primary focus, with corresponding tools, methods, and techniques.
          <em class="card__source source"
            >— via
            <a
              href="https://18f.gsa.gov/2023/05/02/hi-from-the-18F-design-chapter/"
              title="Read at 18F"
              >18F</a
            ></em
          >
        
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card__media">
    <img src="/logos/18f-logo.png" alt="18F logo" />
  </div>
  <div class="card__meta">
    <p class="date">May 02, 2023</p>
  </div>
